FROM aka_title AS aka_t,
   company_name AS cn,
   company_type AS ct,
   info_type AS it1,
   keyword AS k,

   movie_info AS mi,
   movie_keyword AS mk,

AND it1.info = 'release dates'
AND mc.note LIKE '%USA%'
AND mc.note LIKE '%c%'
